## String Formatting

### Use String Templates
```kotlin
// ❌ BAD
Log.d("TAG", "User: " + user.name + " Age: " + user.age)

// ✅ GOOD
Log.d("TAG", "User: ${user.name} Age: ${user.age}")

// ✅ GOOD - for complex expressions
val message = """
    User Details:
    Name: ${user.name}
    Email: ${user.email}
""".trimIndent()
```

